       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. ARITH01.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 WS-BASE-AMOUNT       PIC S9(5)V99 VALUE 120.00.
       01 WS-DISCOUNT          PIC S9(5)V99 VALUE 20.00.
       01 WS-NET               PIC S9(5)V99 VALUE 0.
       01 WS-FACTOR            PIC 9 VALUE 3.
       01 WS-GROSS             PIC S9(5)V99 VALUE 0.
       01 WS-DIVISOR           PIC 9 VALUE 2.
       01 WS-SPLIT             PIC S9(5)V99 VALUE 0.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
           MOVE WS-BASE-AMOUNT TO WS-NET
           SUBTRACT WS-DISCOUNT FROM WS-NET
           MULTIPLY WS-NET BY WS-FACTOR GIVING WS-GROSS
           DIVIDE WS-GROSS BY WS-DIVISOR GIVING WS-SPLIT
           DISPLAY "NET=" WS-NET
           DISPLAY "GROSS=" WS-GROSS
           DISPLAY "SPLIT=" WS-SPLIT
           STOP RUN.
